ABSTRACT
In a cellular communications network having a radio access
network of macrocells and small cells, a mobile device
having a UICC/SIM card is configured to change its dis-
played network name and functionality in accordance with
whether the mobile device has connected to a macrocell or
a small cell. The displayed network name information is
modified to inform the user about new services or data usage
restrictions.
